Debian MavenRepo Indexer 
========================

Debian MavenRepo Indexer is a tool which:
- index /usr/share/maven-repo (ie. local maven repository on Debian-like distribution)
- publish indexes (Lucene) of this repository using nexus-indexer component
- expose some REST services to help query package/classes/artifact relationships

